IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: NAREB is an association of African American real estate professionals that participate in meaningful legal challenges and supports legeslative initiatives that ensure the availability of fair and affordable housing for all americans
IRS990.MissionDesc: NAREB is an association of African American real estate professionals that participate in meaningful legal challenges and supports legeslative initiatives that ensure the availability of fair and affordable housing for all americans
IRS990.Desc: National Association of Real Estate Brokers (NAREB) annual convention and mid-winter conference provided two major forums for professional development, research and the exchange of information among its members as well as the legislature and the general public for the purpose of preserving the right to equal housing oppurtunities. These forums also facilitated the exchange of information between the organizations leadership and is members.

ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp.Desc: NAREB and its affiliates coordinated various membership development activities as well as outreach activities related to affordable housing access and preservation.

ProgSrvcAccomActy3Grp.Desc: Grants to organizations, regional stipends and specific assistance to individuals
